properties.description: Links a type descriptor to the schema that contains it.
Inverse of ComponentOf, from SchemaType to TypeDescriptor.
Connects a type descriptor to its expected property types.
Inverse of InstanceProperties, from PropertyType to TypeDescriptor.
Connects a type descriptor to its expected relationship types.
Inverse of InstanceRelationships, from DeclaredRelationshipType to TypeDescriptor.
Links a holon to the type descriptor that describes it.
Inverse of DescribedBy, from TypeDescriptor to Holon.
Indicates which holon space owns the given holon.
Inverse of OwnedBy, from HolonSpace to Holon.
Links a holon to its properties.
Inverse of Properties, from PropertyType to HolonType.
Specifies the value type constraint for a property.
Inverse of ValueType, from ValueType to PropertyType.
Associates a property type with its symbolic name.
Inverse of PropertyName, from PropertyNameValueType to PropertyType.
Defines the source holon type for a meta relationship type.
Inverse of SourceType, from HolonType to MetaRelationshipType.
Defines the target holon type for a meta relationship type.
Inverse of TargetType, from HolonType to MetaRelationshipType.
Defines the source holon type for a declared relationship type.
Inverse of SourceType, from HolonType to DeclaredRelationshipType.
Defines the source holon type for a inverse relationship type.
Inverse of SourceType, from HolonType to InverseRelationshipType.
Defines the target holon type for a declared relationship type.
Inverse of TargetType, from HolonType to RelationshipType.
Defines the target holon type for a inverse relationship type.
Inverse of TargetType, from HolonType to RelationshipType.
Links an inverse relationship type to the declared relationship it reverses.
Inverse of InverseOf, from DeclaredRelationshipType to InverseRelationshipType.
Declares the allowed symbolic variants of an enum value type.
Inverse of Variants, from EnumVariantType to EnumValueType.
Indicates that one schema holon depends on another.
Inverse of DependsOn, indicating which schemas depend on this one.
Specifies the element value type of a value array.
Inverse of ElementValueType, from ValueType to ValueArrayType.
Inheritance link, this TypeDescriptor extends another TypeDescriptor (single parent).
Inverse of Extends, the parent TypeDescriptor is extended by zero or more children.
Ordered list of PropertyTypes used as positional parameters for template_string ($0, $1, ...).
Inverse of TemplateParameters, indicates that this PropertyType is used as a positional parameter in one or more Format.KeyRuleType instances.
